	 11 AM - 7 PM. Unframed work will be available for purchase from $10-$500\
	, and framed work at 20-50% under its fair market value.\n\nhttps://www.ed
	u.hcponline.org/events/spring-cleaning-print-sale\n\nFrom Houston Center f
